title: Hairdressing logos
content:
Hi,

Can anyone help me identify these two logotypes? I don't think they're custom lettering.

Font: 

 Arcade Interlaced, Cranberry Gin

comments.content:
"IDENTITY": **[Arcade Interlaced](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317112614/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Dafont-1&ffam=Arcade%20Interlaced%20-%20Regular&fid=3e1048ebd1c6e4f9752ae0b3cfe1a7fb&fsize=60&text=IDENTITY&wrap=2)** free font by Yuji Adachi (designed: 1997-2003)

"Sophia": **[Cranberry Gin](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317112614/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Dafont-1&ffam=Cranberry%20Gin%20-%20Regular&fid=eea54229cd7832bdde82e106c6501397&fsize=60&text=Sophia&wrap=2)** free font by Ray Larabie (1998)
Wow, great. Thanks for your help.
